# 1. Code Architecture
- One file = one responsibility. No god files.
- File Size Limits:
  - Component (.tsx): target ≤150 lines, ceiling 200 lines
  - Hook (.tsx): target ≤150 lines, ceiling 200 lines
  - Utility/Service (.ts): target ≤200 lines, ceiling 300 lines
  - Function (within any file): ≤40 lines
  - Hard ceiling: any file ≥300 lines → must split

- Split rules:
  - Split by responsibility only
  - Do NOT split when functionality is cohesive
- Pattern: Single-Function Files + Orchestrator

## 2. AI Behavior
- Assume all questions are questions only
- Only `fix`, `go on`, or `do it` triggers edits
- All changes must include an explanation